https://learn.adafruit.com/node-embedded-development/installing-node-dot-js

To install first time: 

sudo npm install express jade
sudo npm install --unsafe-perm serialport
sudo npm install arest

To run every time power on (or just execute run.sh): 
sudo node app.js

//Navigate to
http://localhost:3000 or http://RPi-ip:3000

source: https://openhomeautomation.net/connect-esp8266-raspberry-pi/
